org.zaproxy.zap.authentication

Interface AuthenticationIndicatorsPanel


  • public interface AuthenticationIndicatorsPanel
    An interface that allows to manipulate the state (content, enabled and tool tip) of fields showing the logged in/out indicators.
    Since:
    2.5.0
